---
import DocsLayout from '../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout
  title="Refund Policy — ToolSnap MCP"
  description="Refund Policy for ToolSnap MCP credits."
  heroTitle="Refund Policy"
  lead="Last updated 2026-07-20."
>
  <div class="legal">
    <p><strong>Credits are non-refundable once purchased.</strong> They do not expire and can be spent at any pace across any paid tool.</p>
    <p>If a purchase was made in error (e.g. duplicate charge) or a tool call failed and was not automatically refunded to your balance, contact <a href="mailto:support@toolsnap.app">support@toolsnap.app</a> within 14 days and we'll review it manually.</p>
    <p>Async media jobs (<code>video_generate</code>): if a render fails after payment, credit and prepaid balances are refunded automatically by the polling tool. Pay-per-call crypto (x402) settles on-chain at submit and cannot be refunded automatically — use credits or prepaid balance for refundable video.</p>
  </div>
</DocsLayout>

<style>
  .legal { color: var(--text); }
  .legal p { color: var(--text-soft); margin-bottom: 1.1em; line-height: 1.7; }
  .legal a { color: var(--cyan-soft); text-decoration: underline; }
</style>
